bDIModel

Class Belief

  • java.lang.Object
    • bDIModel.Belief

  • public class Belief
extends java.lang.Object
    The Belief class instantiates each Belief with initDate, validatedDate and Goal associated with the Belief. The beliefValidate is the Event that validates the Belief.
